{"id":140968,"type":6,"name":"Shazam!","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/36/72/140968_904N9.jpg","rating":{"total":56,"count":{"1":0,"2":1,"3":0,"4":1,"5":9,"6":27,"7":16,"8":1,"9":1,"10":0},"score":6.1},"summary":"每个人身体里都潜藏着一位超级英雄，只需要一点魔力便能将其释放。14岁的街头小混混比利·巴特森(亚瑟·安其饰)通过大喊“沙赞”这个词，就可以变身为成年超级英雄沙赞(扎克瑞·莱维饰)，这是一种来自于古老巫师的恩惠。如神一般的肌肉身体里，仍存有一颗孩子心，他开心地与超能力为伴。他能飞吗？他能X光透视吗？他能从手中射出闪电吗？他能不用再考试了吗？沙赞以孩子般轻率又鲁莽的方式，开始测试他的能力极限。但他需要尽快掌握这些力量，以对抗塞迪斯·希瓦纳博士控制的邪恶势力。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>雷霆沙赞！</li><li><span>放送星期: </span>星期五</li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/24742\">DC Comics</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>奇迹队长</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>神奇上尉</li><li><span>集数: </span>1</li><li><span>开始: </span>2019年4月5日</li><li><span>类型: </span>动作 / 惊悚 / 科幻</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>美国</li><li><span>语言: </span>英语</li><li><span>每集长: </span>132分钟</li><li><span>首播国家: </span>美国</li><li><span>台湾名称: </span>沙赞！</li><li><span>港澳名称: </span>沙赞！神力集结</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt0448115</li><li><span>导演: </span>David F. Sandberg</li><li><span>编剧: </span>Henry Gayden / Darren Lemke / Bill Parker / C.C. Beck</li><li><span>主演: </span>Zachary Levi / Mark Strong / Michelle Borth / Djimon Hounsou / Adam Brody</li>","collection":{"wish":10,"collect":86},"tags":[{"name":"DC","count":25},{"name":"电影","count":22},{"name":"2019","count":8},{"name":"DC扩展宇宙","count":4},{"name":"DCEU","count":3},{"name":"美国","count":3},{"name":"DC.Comics","count":2},{"name":"欧美电影","count":2},{"name":"映画","count":1},{"name":"movie","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":550131,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/550131","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"staff":[{"id":24742,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/f5/df/24742_prsn_rT8SB.jpg","name":"DC漫画","desc":"原作"}],"relations":[{"id":140956,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/67/5d/140956_I41Vx.jpg","title":"Suicide Squad","type":"相同世界观","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/140956"},{"id":140959,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/p